271
00:21:24,287 --> 00:21:26,380
I'm just dead. It's not like
I'm an asshole or anything.

272
00:21:26,456 --> 00:21:28,889
I didn't say
you were an asshole.

273
00:21:28,957 --> 00:21:34,725
