have done something weird to it.

278
00:21:49,510 --> 00:21:52,239
If you don't want it, I'll eat it.

279
00:22:02,187 --> 00:22:05,623
What?

280
00:22:05,691 --> 00:22:08,660
What do you mean, "What?" You just
