296
00:23:01,741 --> 00:23:03,834
I'm sorry.

297
00:23:03,910 --> 00:23:07,174
<i>Hey, look,
it's that dead kid.</i>

298
00:23:07,245 --> 00:23:09,179
It's because I'm dead, isn't it?

299
00:23:09,247 --> 00:23:12,182
